# Knowledge Base & Rules â€“ UI / UX Specification (JSON)

## Design Principles

* Reference-first, not execution-first
* Low cognitive load
* Safe by default (read-only unless explicitly editing)
* Fast search > deep navigation

---

## Knowledge Base UI

```json
{
  "page": "knowledge_base",
  "layout": {
    "type": "three-column",
    "columns": ["categories", "entries", "entry_view"]
  },
  "categories_panel": {
    "title": "Knowledge Domains",
    "items": [
      "Reconnaissance",
      "Enumeration",
      "Exploitation",
      "Post-Exploitation",
      "Services",
      "Ports",
      "Tools",
      "OWASP"
    ],
    "actions": ["add_category"]
  },
  "entries_panel": {
    "search": true,
    "filters": ["tags", "phase", "service"],
    "list_item": {
      "title": "SSH Enumeration",
      "meta": ["phase", "service", "tags"],
      "badges": ["OWASP-A07"]
    },
    "actions": ["add_entry", "import_markdown"]
  },
  "entry_view": {
    "mode": "markdown",
    "read_only_default": true,
    "sections": ["description", "steps", "commands", "notes"],
    "command_block": {
      "copy": true,
      "preview_variables": true
    },
    "actions": ["edit", "duplicate", "link_to_rule"]
  }
}
```

---

## Knowledge Base UX Notes

* Entries open in read-only mode by default
* Editing requires explicit action
* Commands are always copy-only
* Fast keyboard navigation encouraged

---

## Rules UI

```json
{
  "page": "rules",
  "access": "advanced",
  "layout": {
    "type": "two-column",
    "columns": ["rules_list", "rule_editor"]
  },
  "rules_list": {
    "group_by": "phase",
    "list_item": {
      "name": "SSH Enumeration Rule",
      "status": "enabled",
      "badges": ["enumeration", "ssh", "OWASP-A07"]
    },
    "actions": ["toggle_enable", "duplicate_rule"]
  },
  "rule_editor": {
    "mode": "json",
    "schema_validation": true,
    "explain_rule": true,
    "sections": {
      "metadata": true,
      "conditions": true,
      "suggestions": true
    },
    "safety": {
      "no_execution": true,
      "read_only_default": true,
      "confirm_on_edit": true
    },
    "actions": ["edit", "validate", "save"]
  }
}
```

---

## Rule UX Safeguards

* Rules are hidden behind Advanced toggle
* JSON schema validation required
* Human-readable explanation rendered
* No live execution impact without save

---

## Cross-Integration UX

```json
{
  "integration": {
    "from_knowledge_base": ["link_to_rule", "suggest_in_engagement"],
    "from_rules": ["open_related_kb", "preview_suggestions"]
  }
}
```

---

## UX Summary

* Knowledge Base = fast reference library
* Rules = powerful but protected system brain
* Clear separation from live engagement work
* Designed for both junior learning and senior control
